<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>1、低位锤形线</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201117/db20a624b00b4912bd0db06fbe3e73de.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这种形态一般出现在下跌通道当中。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">买点：出现次日，收盘价能够越过锤形线实体。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">止损参考位：锤形线最低点。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>2、低位十字星</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201117/55d00a7f6fac42cab32af9776ddd2658.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">买点：低位十字星出现次日，股价上涨越过十字星实体。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">止损参考位：十字星最低点。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>3、低位倒锤线</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">买点：出现的次日，收盘价越过锤形线实体。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">止损参考位：倒锤形线最低点。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
