<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>4、看涨捉腰带</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201117/d241b97db6564ab89b811ff0317cc44c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">买点：看涨捉腰带线出现次日，若股价未创新低，则构成买点。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">止损参考位：捉腰带线最低位。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>5、低位螺旋桨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201117/bfb71fe9cf60484d87e45cd24866e0f5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">买点：低位螺旋桨线出现次日，若股价上涨越过螺旋桨实体，则构成买点。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">止损参考位：螺旋桨线最低位。</p>
